Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}“ベラドンナ”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}な… なんで？　私の… 命令を…
